22
00:01:42,260 --> 00:01:44,850
=Episode 17=

23
00:02:28,819 --> 00:02:30,862
Shanshan hasn't come back all day.

24
00:02:31,620 --> 00:02:33,699
I already had Li look after her.

25
00:02:34,387 --> 00:02:35,290
You, on the other hand,

26
00:02:35,500 --> 00:02:37,699
have been moping in this room all day.

27
00:02:37,699 --> 00:02:39,300
Are you still the Zhuang Yan I know?

28
00:02:44,620 --> 00:02:45,300
Are you hungry?

29
00:02:47,819 --> 00:02:48,099
Mm.

30
00:02:49,020 --> 00:02:50,539
Get up and take a hot shower.

31
00:02:50,700 --> 00:02:51,900
I'll make you something to eat.

32
00:02:53,500 --> 00:02:54,340
You hear me?

33
00:02:56,659 --> 00:02:57,100
Mm.

34
00:03:03,099 --> 00:03:04,020
Hurry up.

35
00:03:39,419 --> 00:03:40,220
Don't move.

36
00:03:40,660 --> 00:03:43,262
If you get sick, I'll have to take you
to the hospital for a jab.

37
00:03:56,539 --> 00:03:57,419
Don't move.

38
00:03:58,020 --> 00:04:00,620
If you get sick,
I'll take you to the hospital for a jab.

39
00:04:02,512 --> 00:04:08,200
笙ｪFaded smiles burning bright笙ｪ

40
00:04:09,387 --> 00:04:14,800
笙ｪI run back along the dates笙ｪ

41
00:04:16,980 --> 00:04:17,980
This is my head,

42
00:04:17,980 --> 00:04:19,180
