43
00:04:19,980 --> 00:04:21,500
Why are you so clumsy?

44
00:04:22,420 --> 00:04:24,540
Didn't you raise Qin Jiamin
all by yourself?

45
00:04:24,699 --> 00:04:25,980
You never dried her hair before?

46
00:04:26,180 --> 00:04:27,180
I'm her brother,

47
00:04:27,180 --> 00:04:28,180
