48
00:04:28,720 --> 00:04:30,139
Besides, I was busy making a living.

49
00:04:30,420 --> 00:04:31,960
How would I have time to dry her hair?

50
00:04:36,850 --> 00:04:41,375
笙ｪSo you won't get wet
when you turn around笙ｪ

51
00:04:42,940 --> 00:04:44,219
Dry it like this.

52
00:04:45,390 --> 00:04:47,400
Do it a few more times,
and you'll get used to it.

53
00:04:49,312 --> 00:04:52,312
笙ｪLet the hourglass flow backward笙ｪ

54
00:04:52,437 --> 00:04:56,387
笙ｪI travel against time笙ｪ

55
00:04:56,537 --> 00:05:02,525
笙ｪAll regrets deserve to be remeasured笙ｪ

56
00:05:02,737 --> 00:05:07,050
笙ｪAt the crossroads of fate笙ｪ

57
00:05:07,325 --> 00:05:10,900
笙ｪThat moment is eternal笙ｪ

58
00:05:11,000 --> 00:05:13,375
笙ｪThe counter-clockwise hand笙ｪ

59
00:05:13,900 --> 00:05:17,137
笙ｪIs ultimately nailed笙ｪ

60
00:05:17,912 --> 00:05:21,150
笙ｪTo eternity笙ｪ

61
00:05:28,680 --> 00:05:30,880
There's nothing much going on
at the office these days.

62
00:05:30,900 --> 00:05:32,339
I had Li get you a leave of absence.

63
00:05:33,339 --> 00:05:34,339
What are your plans?

64
00:05:38,980 --> 00:05:39,940
No idea.

65
00:05:42,379 --> 00:05:43,980
You've been in Haicheng for so long.

66
00:05:44,019 --> 00:05:45,790
Either thinking about
dealing with Zhou Zeyang,

67
00:05:45,819 --> 00:05:47,290
or solving one problem after another.

68
00:05:47,830 --> 00:05:49,600
You haven't really looked around,
have you?

69
00:05:50,137 --> 00:05:50,656
Mm.

70
00:05:51,750 --> 00:05:52,339
How about this?

71
00:05:52,880 --> 00:05:54,940
After you finish your noodles,
I'll show you around.

72
00:06:03,819 --> 00:06:05,379
Slow down. You'll choke.

73
00:06:22,700 --> 00:06:26,975
笙ｪRewind to 1995,
back to the street we met笙ｪ

74
00:06:26,975 --> 00:06:30,275
笙ｪWind blows through the sycamore leaves
and lands on your shoulder笙ｪ

75
00:06:30,350 --> 00:06:34,650
笙ｪI wish I could pause and stop time笙ｪ

76
00:06:34,713 --> 00:06:38,363
笙ｪLet unspoken love
be preserved forever as amber笙ｪ

77
00:06:38,363 --> 00:06:41,925
笙ｪRewind to 1995,
gentle touch of fingertips笙ｪ

78
00:06:41,975 --> 00:06:45,238
笙ｪStar sparks in your eyes burn my chest笙ｪ

79
00:06:45,238 --> 00:06:48,988
笙ｪThis looping script
is beyond my saving笙ｪ

80
00:06:48,988 --> 00:06:52,762
笙ｪOnly stories in reverse,
