81
00:06:52,862 --> 00:06:55,687
笙ｪNo new scenes笙ｪ

82
00:06:56,262 --> 00:07:00,300
笙ｪFarewell to 1995,
love is a flood I can never return笙ｪ

83
00:07:00,400 --> 00:07:04,000
笙ｪI keep revisiting
the negatives of my memories笙ｪ

84
00:07:04,062 --> 00:07:09,050
笙ｪIf time could turn back,
would the answer stay the same?笙ｪ

85
00:07:17,620 --> 00:07:20,459
I didn't expect Haicheng in the 1990s
to be such a nice place to stall.

86
00:07:21,262 --> 00:07:22,663
The technology is a bit behind.

87
00:07:23,012 --> 00:07:24,375
I can't see the photos right away.

88
00:07:24,987 --> 00:07:27,708
I really miss having smartphones
thirty years later.

89
00:07:27,787 --> 00:07:29,626
You can look at pictures instantly.

90
00:07:31,237 --> 00:07:34,037
Why do you always talk about the 1990s?

91
00:07:34,100 --> 00:07:35,981
Like you're not from this era.

92
00:07:36,025 --> 00:07:38,665
I mean, in another thirty years,

93
00:07:38,665 --> 00:07:40,624
