will grow explosively.

94
00:07:40,980 --> 00:07:43,139
Life will become incredibly convenient.

95
00:07:43,219 --> 00:07:45,812
You won't need to go out to eat.

96
00:07:45,850 --> 00:07:50,375
When you shop,
you won't need to carry cash.

97
00:07:52,880 --> 00:07:53,725
You don't believe me?

98
00:07:56,019 --> 00:07:56,500
I do.

99
00:07:57,112 --> 00:07:58,272
I believe everything you say.

100
00:08:23,180 --> 00:08:23,899
Wait here.

101
00:08:28,660 --> 00:08:30,500
Where are you going?

102
00:08:41,739 --> 00:08:42,540
Manying!

103
00:09:00,470 --> 00:09:01,910
I've been looking everywhere for you.

104
00:09:04,099 --> 00:09:06,339
Why are you wandering around
instead of going home?

105
00:09:06,780 --> 00:09:08,940
I can't find the way home.

106
00:09:14,780 --> 00:09:15,579
Remember this.

107
00:09:16,562 --> 00:09:18,512
If you can't find your way home,

108
00:09:18,850 --> 00:09:20,725
walk toward wherever there's light.

109
00:09:33,437 --> 00:09:36,749
笙ｪUnder the dim lights, our eyes meet笙ｪ

